      right: ["Papilledema with blurred disc margins and venous engorgement (elevated ICP)","Proliferative retinopathy with neovascularization and vitreous hemorrhage","Flame-shaped hemorrhages with cotton-wool spots (malignant hypertensive retinopathy)","Cherry-red spot at macula (central retinal artery occlusion - emergent)","Retinal detachment: pale elevated retina with loss of red reflex","Cup-to-disc ratio >0.7 with visual field loss (advanced glaucoma)"]
